Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,《纸牌屋》前情提要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果明天有人朝我开枪  那绝不会是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If a bullet comes my way tomorrow, it will not be an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我得赶快躲开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I must be quick to duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道格兰特将军是如何击败李将军的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know how Grant defeated Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他的人更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had more men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他愿意让他们去送死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he was willing to let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是屠杀  而非策略  赢得了战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was butchery, not strategy, which won the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前酗酒  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You used to be an alcoholic, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-酒瘾是戒不掉的    -你怀念这味道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not "used to be."   - Do you miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个都让我很失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've both disappointed me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  你还在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他20年来第一次挂掉我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the first time he's ever hung up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真为你难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚跟一个叫赛斯·格雷森的人通了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just got off the phone with a guy named Seth Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马博利医生有没有为克莱尔·安德伍德做过堕胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Dr. Marbury perform an abortion for Claire Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一本日记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He kept a journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这日记就是我的简历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That journal is my version of a resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会成功的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没选择了  但你还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have a choice, but you still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你想进去看看  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanted to see inside one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,务必做得干净利落  道格 一击致命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This needs to be clean, Doug. One fall of the ax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-趴在地上    -立刻趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- On the ground.   - On the ground now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  杀戮开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the butchery begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在面临能源危机  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got an energy crisis, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now what the White House needs to --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,总统选择对中国保持强硬态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president chose to remain tough on China.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不  那是被你逼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You forced him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你选择了冯  是你让我和他见面的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You chose Feng. You're the one who put me in a room with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,厨子手艺不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cook can't blame his ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不能去怪原料差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if he doesn't like how they taste together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果钐的价格不降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Samarium prices don't reduce,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,市场只能随之上调电价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the market will have no choice but to compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那样对每一个使用空调的人来说都是坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's bad for everyone who owns an air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去找总统本人谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should speak to the president himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,总统最近不是很重视我的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president hasn't placed much value on my advice lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一样  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm in the same boat as you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的是  你和他的办公室只隔三道门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Difference being you've got an office three doors down from the Oval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们同心协力吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's work together, for Christ sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意  我可以忘记斯波特瑟尔维尼亚的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm wiling to put Spotsylvania behind us if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那你会去跟他谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you'll talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我开会要迟到了  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm late for a meeting, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,答应还是不答应  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes or no, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能保证他听得进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't guarantee he'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是答应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,总比不答应强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's better than a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,称职的拳击手都能看出对手什么时候不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any pugilist worth his salt knows when someone's on the ropes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候就该果断连续出拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's when you throw a combination to the gut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,左勾拳直击下颚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a left hook to the jaw.
