Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,钐的价格他们绝不会让步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Samarium is the last thing they'll let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能源价格一直涨  他们就有谈判筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As long as our energy prices rise, they have the leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们只是静观其变呢  跟他们比瞪眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't we offer nothing? Move toward attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果中国不参加再融资债券拍卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If China doesn't show at the refunding auction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,长期利率会一路飙升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}long-term interest rates will spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一个星期后我们的十年期国债\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in a week yields on our 10-year notes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,将突破7%大关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will pierce the seven-percent threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们现在妥协  那就是必然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if we go soft now, that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我们应该强硬一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,至少应该考虑一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should at least consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,中国人不吃敬酒  我们就上罚酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Chinese don't like carrots. Let's see how they like the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what might that look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,增加粮食检查的频率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could raise inspection rates on foodstuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们的粮食扣在港口直到腐烂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold them in our ports till they rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,提高多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much of a raise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想要有效果要提高20%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}20% if we want to draw blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用增加抽查次数的方式进行掩饰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bury the move with increased spot checks all the way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这类措施不能解决眼前的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These sort of tactics don't solve the immediate problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,人们现在交着三倍的电费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People are paying triple the standard rate for electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到八月份  就是五倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll hit a five-fold increase by August.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你  总统先生  通过行政命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if you, Mr. President, by executive order,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,从第三方手里购买钐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}purchase Samarium through a third party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,绕过中国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut the Chinese out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,迫使他们提高全球价格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Force them to either raise their prices worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,或是降低价格维持跟我们的交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or lower them to keep direct flow with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  对外宣称是为了国防需要进行钐储备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We stockpile Samarium for denfense purposes, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后悄悄的把多余的钐卖给我们核能源方面的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And quietly sell what we don't need to our friends in nuclear energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,以优惠价格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,核能源补助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A subsidy for nuclear power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱人相互接济  这别人会怎么看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The richest of the rich? How's that gonna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在面对国家危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're dealing with a national crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能受公众舆论的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't get sidetracked with public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这能让中国知道我们愿意耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would show China we're willing to wait this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有这份钱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do we have the resources?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要计算一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd have to run the numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,预期波动  考虑不同模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anticipate fluctuations, consider different models --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,估计一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your best guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有  可以进行中度储备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do. For a moderate stockpile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  以国防部名义起草请求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Draw up a request from the Defense Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-是  先生    -琳达  起草行政命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir.    - Linda, draft the executive order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜  确保我们能找到一个第三方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Cathy, make sure we have a third-party conduit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,购买钐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to purchase the Samarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跟印度买吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll go through India.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那巴基斯坦可要不高兴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that won't fly well with Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会提前告知他们  只要及时告知他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll alert them in advance. As long as they're in the loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就没什么问题  我们又不欠他们什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll be all right. Not that we owe them any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  开始工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,贝茜  还加上E条款下的三条罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Betsy. Three additional counts under Section E?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,三条已经很少了  反映了对犯罪意图的狭义解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three is low. It reflects a narrow interpretation of criminal intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的委托人入侵了数据中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your client broke into a data center.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你能提供什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会认罪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not doing a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来处理这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不想开庭审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't want a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我能在公开法庭上高声提出的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The questions I'll be raising loud and clear in open court...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡斯  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lucas, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也有问题  古德温先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have our own questions, Mr. Goodwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,比如  你怎么会有这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For example, what were you doing with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是在你公寓发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德拍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underwood took them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得陪审团能信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you really expect a jury to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是他  他们有一腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He did. They were having an affair --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只会如实看待这些证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or are they gonna see them for what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你迷恋巴恩斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proof of our obsession with Ms. Barnes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还编出一套荒唐的阴谋论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the ludicrous conspiracy you have concocted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来解释她的死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to explain her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell us what you're offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你委托人供认以下罪名  E条款下一条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your client pleads to one count under Section E
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,闯入数据中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for breaking into a data center,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欺诈一条  偷《先驱报》的密码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one count for fraud, for stealing the password from the Herald.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,第一项获罪10年  第二项10年  同时计算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}10 years under Section E. 10 years for fraud. Served concurrently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,服刑7年可假释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eligible for parole in seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想单独跟委托人谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to speak to my client, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请关掉录像录音设备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cameras and recording equipment off, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我介绍总统  他来介绍你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll introduce the president, then he'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他在  就不能点名军方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he's there, we can't mention the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只能说全国皆有这种现象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the endemic problem nationwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  那再过一遍讲词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. So we should go through these speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看还有没有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and make sure that there's nothing --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沃克夫人  你找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Walker, you asked for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要确认一下总统能不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to confirm whether the president's going
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去新奥尔良\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make it to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是这周五吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This Friday, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但我知道他今早有内阁会议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. But I know he had a cabinet meeting this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去和琳达沟通一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to Linda right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你希望加勒特去  可能源危机的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you want Garrett there. But with this energy crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你非说不可了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, now you have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是向来不太喜欢克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've just never been very fond of her. Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得·罗素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter Russo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不太喜欢跟老板上床的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just have a thing about women who sleep with their bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我相信他们是真心相爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway, I'm sure whatever they had was genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也不关我事  只要她工作做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's none of my business, 'cause if she's doing a good job,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其他也无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's all that matters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特还挺满意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett seems to think she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不多嘴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I should just keep my feelings to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果总统不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if the president is not able to be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对咱们或许也是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could be a silver lining for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不用给军方留面子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won't have to hold back with the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,电话监听  视频监控  预谋犯罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phone taps. Video surveillance. Premeditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,长期动机  你没希望的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sustained intent. They've got you cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我认罪  就没人知道真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I plead out, that's it. No one hears the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认罪的话  根本没人会听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't plead, no one will hear you, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一直到你七八十岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not until you're in your 70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你和汉默施密特谈了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you talked to Hammerschmidt yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你没资格谈条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in no position to make demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了又不算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你只会惹恼他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All you'll do is piss them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个交易很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've got a good deal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到你的行为  算很不错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A great deal, considering what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他们没改主意  赶紧接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should take it before their change their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆·汉默施密特  我要跟他谈  否则就上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom Hammerschmidt. I talk to him, or we're going to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请抬起胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raise your arms, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有什么物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,项链\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My neck chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请掏出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  我还得解领带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? I gotta take off my tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,必须看一下  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to see it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,虔诚的基督徒啊  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a good Christian, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲的  是她虔诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother's. She was the good Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也是个好儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then you're just the good son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,外面热吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hot out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,96华氏度  车里显示的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}96, according to my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以前在加夫尼也这么热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had heat like that back in Gaffney,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那会儿还没有空调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we didn't know what air conditioning was,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为夏天就该这么难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we just accepted as fact that summer was meant to be miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,加不加水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neat or with water?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只要水  不要酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the water. You can hold the bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,得找个解决办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to find a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好让这个夏天美国人民不那么难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that this one isn't miserable for 300 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我有办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already have found a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧  弗兰克  钐补助吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, please, Frank. A Samarium subsidy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是你还是雷蒙德表示怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that your skepticism or Raymond's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我  估计他也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mine. Anticipating his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩还没谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you haven't spoken to him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想向他提出他会同意的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to offer him something he can agree to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他没什么选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he doesn't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要把他逼入绝境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you cornering him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我把价钱减半  这是在帮他啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm cutting the rate by half. I'd call that liberating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他可不这么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know that's not how he'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这场贸易战让北京方面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This trade war is preventing the refinery
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,迟迟不批准精炼厂项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from being approved in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,目前  他跟冯的合资项目不是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His co-venture with Feng is not our highest priority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,稀土精炼厂能一劳永逸地解决这场危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A rare earth refinery solves this crisis permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是三年之后了  这个夏天还是难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three years from now. Not this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不止如此  实施核能补助他至多不赔不赚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just that. With the subsidy he'll break even at best,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫做生意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's no point in doing business to hover between red and black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德的利益对我来说比他的合资项目更不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond's profits are an even lower priority to me than his co-venture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的目的  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you're up to, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟塔斯克叫劲又得不到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing to gain by locking horn with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,问你的客户去  是塔斯克在叫劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask your client. It's Tusk who's locking the horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他不喜欢矛盾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not a man who likes conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就提出要求吧  我知道你不在乎核能补助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then make the ask. 'Cause I know you don't care about the subsidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有更大的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个虔诚的基督徒  雷米  跟你母亲一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a good Christian, Remy, like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我想要别的  我会如实说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would tell you the truth if I wanted more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在发出信号吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You trying to send a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那内容是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,顽固比顺从的代价更大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That stubbornness is far more costly than obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你站错队了  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're on the wrong side, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我们中肯定有一人站错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, one of us sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大黄蜂飞回家后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when the bumblebee flew home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,发现它的朋友们都抱着大桶蜂蜜在等他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all his friends were waiting with buckets honey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他的朋友有蠕虫  老鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's got his worm friend and his mouse friend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛和蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his spider friend and his snail friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它们都有许多蜂蜜  他看上去开心多了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they all had tons of honey. And he looks happier now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊    -是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah!   - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他们开心地嗡嗡叫了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so they all buzzzzed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你和朋友们在一起  生活会甜蜜得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because life is sweet when you spend it with your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会振动翅膀发出嗡鸣声吗  扇动小翅膀吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you all buzz your wings? Buzz your little wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-我觉得会发出颤动的声音  就像    -就像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I think it would make a fluttering noise, like...   - like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的颤动呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your flutters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,外面太热了  你不该抛球  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's too hot out here for you to be doing this, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm keeping hydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这距离满足规定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that even regulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只到一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only half.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想让媒体看到我在大街上练习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't want the press to see practicing on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得你在格林维尔开球那次吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember when you threw out that first pitch in Greenville?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在想你什么时候会提到那事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wondering how long it was gonna take you to bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那次还不是全国电视台直播呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wasn't even on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,格林维尔发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened in Greenville?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,格林维尔驱动队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Greenville Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,红袜队的1A队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Single A team for the Red Sox.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,主场作战  我站在投球区土墩上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a home game. I get on the mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你从土墩上抛球吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You threw from the mound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想投个好球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I wanted to throw a real pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没抛好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,差得远呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一半吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halfway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,球在我松手前滑了出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ball slipped out of my hand just before I released it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,直线抛上了天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Went straight up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,掉下来砸在我头上  全场爆发大笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hit me on top of the head. The whole stadium burst a gut laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,喜剧性投球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comic relief pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真会说话  密查姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's very clever, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tell Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他们处的真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're really good with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们作手指画时  你看到罗比了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see Robbie when they were finger-painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他脱掉了裤子  把他自己涂成蓝色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He pulled down his pants and started painting himself blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-没看到    -真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿我都洗干净了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope I got it all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利克斯和达利尔不会在意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure Alex and Daria don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是让他光着身子四处跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They let him run around naked all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  但不会像光屁股的蓝精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but probably not with his Smurf ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do we want to do for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一些吃剩的鸡肉  或者我们可以叫披萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got some leftover chicken. Or we could order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,披萨  不做菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pizza. No dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全忘了有个朋友今晚要来接我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I -- I totally forgot I've got a friend picking me up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I -- I completely blanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-没事    -我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's fine.   - I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不必道歉  是你男朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't sweat it. Is it, uh, your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  只是一个老朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. Um, just an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我能见见他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点害羞  我不知道他是否愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's kinda shy. I do-- I don't know if he'd be up for --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Totally cool. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们改天再一起吃晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll just do dinner another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你知道去哪里找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You know where I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,几个月了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能去教堂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't go to church?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟任何人有接触都可能暴露我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anywhere you interact with other people opens us up to risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就该整天闷在呼叫中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. I'm just supposed to slave away at the fucking call center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,或是待在公寓里不出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then lock myself in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么小题大做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't get dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  没有什么可担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? There -- there's nothing to worry about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果谁林奇堡的亲戚来访就能毁了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All it takes is one person's cousin to visit from Lynchburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是你的高中同学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone you went to high school with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是曾跟你共度良宵的客户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or some client that you spend the night with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人才不会出现在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those guys would never end up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不就跑来这里了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ended up here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你能  你是个坚强的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you can. You're a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些  这就是全部了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it? That's everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你以前就听过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. You've heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个朋友  卢卡斯  而不是记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a friend, Lucas. Not as a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会接着挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我去打电话  去跑腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I make the phone calls. I do the legwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They treating you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是问那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常想达成认罪协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're pushing the plea deal pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在认真考虑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How seriously are you considering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看文章的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to see how this article impacts things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的律师怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does your lawyer say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得这是个坏主意  我应该认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He thinks that's a bad idea. That I should take the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该听他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you should listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我要文章  我确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I want the article. That I'm certain of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我得赶快开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I better get to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我会像对待其他报道一样对待这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna treat this the way I would any other story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,报道事实  你也许不会喜欢我写的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever the facts bear. You might not like what I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会先让你看  然后你再做决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you read it first. Then you can decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,挺住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我擦掉吗  求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you wipe this off? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,其他核供应商都赞同吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the other nuclear providers are on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分  除了雷蒙德的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most. Except Raymond's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有几个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couple of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,湖港核电站  狼泉集团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lakeport Nuclear. Wolf Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法证明  但我敢肯定他们是串通好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I can't prove it, but I am absolutely sure they're colluding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德想让我丢脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond wants to embarrass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我提出方案  核能说客却不肯合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I offer a solution, nuclear lobby turns its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他有拒绝的权利  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has the right to refuse, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但他没法操纵能源市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What he cannot do is manipulate the energy market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你想对经销方施压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to put pressure on the distribution side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅施压  彻底禁止纵向合并\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than pressure. Ban vertical integration entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有那个管制权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have that regulatory power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给《紧急能源法案》加一条反垄断协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We add an antitrust agreement to the Emergency Energy Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打破地区性供应和经销垄断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We break up the regional supply and distribution monopolies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就像当年对贝尔系统那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like the Bell System.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs14\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}1984年  司法部结束了贝尔公司对电话服务的垄断  将一个大公司拆分为独立小公司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那马上就会引起官司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be challenged immediately in the courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要协议通过  只是用来吓唬人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't need it to pass. We just need to threaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看他会不会屈服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if he falls into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这事能不能低调办妥  不闹上新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a way to do that without it making its way into the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望世界上最有钱的有钱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want the world's wealthiest one percent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on my phone sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is absolutely a way to do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的酒来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,周二晚上就这么热闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crowded for a Tuesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把室温保持在18度  而且免费\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We keep it at 65 degrees. And it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯伏特加苏打水18块也叫免费吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you call 18 bucks for a vodka soda free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那也比电力公司的账单便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still cheaper than a Pepco bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那要看你喝多少了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Depends on how many you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我们喝醉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You trying to get us drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝得越醉  给的小费越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drunker you are, bigger your tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不用喝醉就会好好答谢优质服务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have to be drunk to appreciate good service.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找零钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真不要脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我是个好说客  干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes me a good lobbyist. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬  举动很大胆  但是没用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, Jackie, bold move, but it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们可以轻松通过这项修正案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know we can pass this amendment in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许  但没有人会遵守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe. But no one'll comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它会被推翻  最后竹篮打水一场空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll get overturned. Big fuss for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会被推翻  但依然会留下印记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might get overturned. But it gets ink along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以我对雷蒙德·塔斯克的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One thing I learned about Raymond Tusk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不在乎什么公众意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is he doesn't two bird shits about public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他的股东们在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His stockholders do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'd jump in a pit of snakes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会跳进蛇窝  把自己点燃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and light themselves on fire if he gave the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你能转达我们的意图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I'm asking if that you convey our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么找我  弗兰克打个电话还不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why me? Frank could easily pick up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你还叫他弗兰克呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still call him Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不会当面叫  我也尽量避免见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to his face, which I try to keep to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得在白宫有个能说上话的人很好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you appreciate having an ear in the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是那样还好了  但最近我净听他说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't, if I had an ear. But lately all I've got is a mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  他不是很善于倾听  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. He's not the best listener, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是为他工作就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try working for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾在他手下干过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were on his staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,八年  新闻发言人  那时你还没进入国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eight years. Press secretary. Before you joined Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒说明了很多问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That explains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比如什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比如很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我就当你是在羞辱我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take that as an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这就走吗  这就撇下我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it? You're abandoning me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我去买下一轮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I'm buying the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,礼尚往来嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't accept gifts from lobbyists without reciprocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我是个好帮手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plus, I'm a good wingman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你能多跟那个酒吧女侍接触\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This gets you more face time with the barmaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗莱迪烧烤餐馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你都做好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You already got 'em ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手下通知我你要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your guys gave me the heads-up you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他们没有太早吵醒你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I hope that they didn't wake you earlier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,操  这么热我哪能睡得着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck, man. With this heat I ain't sleeping much anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  家里没有空调吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? No AC at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我有空调  只是不想付账单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I got a unit. I just don't want to pay the damn bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总的来说  这里的温度还可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too bad in here, all things considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我们在阴凉处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's 'cause we in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,过两小时  你要是去外面人行道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you get outside a couple hours from now on that pavement,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,滚烫的地面能把你的鸡巴烤熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fry your damn dick off from three feet below.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,烧烤架那边一定很难熬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must be bad over that grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我都觉不出区别了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't tell the difference no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you what, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,气温超过37度  这里的情况就会变糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stuff goes down aroundhere when the mercury pop a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,之前在家里打老婆的男人会到街上来打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Man who beat his wife at home will beat her right out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们的兽性都暴露出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brings out the animal in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It ain't no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我会被什么惊醒  枪声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What used to wake me up? Gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道现在是什么吗  人们操的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you know what does? People fucking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,又是呻吟又是尖叫  像巷子里的猫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moaning and screaming like god damn cats in the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好  天热一身汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what they say: When you get hot and sweaty,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,脱衣就开干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it make you ripe and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都喝多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚的事没发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门之后  一切公事公办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I walk out that door, it's business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有特殊优待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  你不需要申请禁制令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. You won't need a restraining order.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我很惊讶  你没去找那个女招待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised you didn't go for the waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你比她性感得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're much sexier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她为小费工作  而你运作国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She works for tips. You run Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那也比她厉害得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's half more than she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那么不是我的身体吸引你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's not my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那双腿还是挺不错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those legs don't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是满口胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're so full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  是你的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. It's your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让我欲罢不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把塔斯克的意思转达给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me know what Tusk has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不谈公事  你还没出门呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Business hasn't started. You haven't walked out that door yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雷米·丹顿  \N公事：跟雷·塔谈过了  他说法庭上见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小约翰在移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little John on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们提高赌注  把联邦能源管理委员会拉进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We raise the bet. We get FERC involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,调查吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要国会来调用能源委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't need Congress to activate the Regulatory Commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是价格听证  会耗费好几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a price-fixing review? That would take months.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一次  只是威胁  不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again, it's the threat. Not the actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他会采用同样的对策\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll employ the same logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把这事拿到法庭上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Draw it out. Fight back with appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果联邦能源管理委员会开始行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he'll have to divulge his accounting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他的账目就会曝光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if FERC takes action.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有哪个生意人愿意公开账目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, no businessman wants to open up his books,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是430亿的账目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially one with $43 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这事开始失控了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is getting outta hand, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不应该跟雷蒙德对着干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shouldn't be duking it out with Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是他想要的  让自己回到圈里来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's exactly what he wants. To force himself back into the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.48,0:24:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把他排除在外有什么好处呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's to be gained by shutting him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给他个教训  让他知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The simple lesson that you cannot strong-arm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能强迫美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能沦落到跟他斗气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't devolve to a pissing contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给雷蒙德打电话  邀他来华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna call Raymond. Invite him to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你彻底投降  否则他不会接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't accept anything but total surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm making the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别把自己逼到那个地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't put yourself in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道如何维护政府的尊严  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how to maintain the integrity of my office. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.47,0:24:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.35,0:24:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要跟总统待两分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two minutes with the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克就能再获青睐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Tusk may be back in his good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要阻止他们再度联手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to disrupt the nuptials and prevent a second marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.88,0:25:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  你看上去棒极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.58,0:25:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.55,0:25:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are things?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  琳达让我忙得脚不着地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. Linda works me to the bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.36,0:25:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's what I signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.89,0:25:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  你干得很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, from what I've heard, you're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.14,0:25:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能听到这样的评价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's really nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.39,0:25:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你谈谈特莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I wanted to talk to you about Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.35,0:25:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定注意到她仍在适应自己的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you've noticed that she's still sort of adjusting to her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.18,0:25:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说自信方面吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean her confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该主动去找她谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it would be great if you reached out to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.82,0:25:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让她知道如果有什么需要你会帮助她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just let her know that you're there if there's anything that she needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.19,0:25:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实跟她不熟  我们见过  但是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really know her that well. I mean, we've met, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.98,0:25:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.22,0:25:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或者就告诉她  你很喜欢为总统工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe just tell her that you enjoy working for the president
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意尽你所能帮助她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're there to be of help to her in any way you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.41,0:25:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不觉得那样有点唐突吗    -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You don't think that's a little -- I don't know -- brash?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.39,0:25:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这么去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me to just approach her like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《华盛顿先驱报》前雇员佐伊·巴恩斯加入头条网
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.62,0:25:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}杜兰特部门
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.02,0:26:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}罗素获得党鞭办公室支持  竞选州长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}议员得到副总统支持
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.41,0:26:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你已接通斯克斯基宅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've reached the Skorsky residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.96,0:26:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请在哔声后留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又是汤姆·汉默施密特  还是要找简宁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom Hammerschmidt again. Still trying to reach Janine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.11,0:26:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还是重要的事  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still important. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.59,0:26:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.68,0:26:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,汉默施密特整天都在往我们新闻处打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hammerschmidt's been calling our press office all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.18,0:26:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你一样不希望闹出任何新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want a story to come out any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.41,0:27:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我们损失一名重要线人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We lose a major asset if it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.34,0:27:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能以安保理由让他噤声吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you squash it for security reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.77,0:27:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦让媒体知道就不行了  第一修正案什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not once it's been shared with the press. First Amendment crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.34,0:27:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,牢房并没能解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ward isn't making things any easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.49,0:27:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她想邀个大功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants a notch in her belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.43,0:27:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给她一个机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're giving her one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.73,0:27:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是古德温  她想要奥尔西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not Goodwin. She wants Orsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,六年的首要通缉犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most Wanted list for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.01,0:27:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搞定汉默施密特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll handle Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.16,0:27:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你得确保古德温认罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to make sure Goodwin takes the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.58,0:27:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,35年刑期  不许假释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If 35 with no parole doesn't scare the piss out of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.18,0:27:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对能吓倒他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what will.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.47,0:27:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别去吓唬他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then don't try to scare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.45,0:27:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让他彻底绝望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remove hope from equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.04,0:27:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力控制这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried to keep this contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.18,0:27:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我没预料到汉默施密特会出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't anticipate Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.89,0:27:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,斯克斯基女士跟他合作了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Ms. Skorsky cooperating with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.55,0:27:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他给她打过电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我在联调局的朋友说他们没交谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My guy at the bureau said they haven't actually spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,至少没在电话里交谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least not on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.45,0:27:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果闹上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this goes to court...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:27:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That won't happen, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.68,0:27:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他发表了文章就会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will if he publishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.79,0:28:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我来找你是因为我无法控制汉默施密特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm bringing this to you because I can't control Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.47,0:28:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.91,0:28:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要发动正面进攻  然后守住阵线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to invite a full-frontal attack. Then hold the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.01,0:28:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟他谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.77,0:28:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,面对面  只有我们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Face to face. Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.17,0:28:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那不是个好主意  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think that's a good idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.47,0:28:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有更好的主意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.09,0:28:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法避免战争  但我们可以选择战场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't avoid the battle, but we can choose the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.99,0:28:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把会面安排在白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.80,0:28:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,摆架子吓唬他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll intimidate him with formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.61,0:28:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.13,0:28:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你没有耐心听道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you don't have patience for apologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.19,0:28:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很抱歉让你失望了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm sorry if I've let you down in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.59,0:28:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们集中精神解决眼前问题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's concentrate on what's in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.39,0:28:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我安排好之后会告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know when I have a time set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.70,0:28:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-越快越好    -是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Soon as possible.   - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.35,0:29:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这算是长篇报道的概述吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So this is a sort of outline to the larger piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.65,0:29:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,问题都在下一页\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With questions on the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.54,0:29:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在是私下谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对  私下谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.04,0:29:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆  我知道你关心这个年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Tom, I know that you care about this young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也尊重你的职业精神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I respect you as a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.89,0:29:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But these questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.43,0:29:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不直接问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you just ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.61,0:29:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不再掐死别人家宠物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I stopped strangling people's pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  罗素议员的死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, the death of Congressman Russo --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.89,0:29:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我的朋友  彼得·罗素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean my friend, Peter Russo,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的自杀让两个年幼的孩子失去了父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whose suicide left two small children with no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不会回答关于那事的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I will not answer questions about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.39,0:29:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我知道  不  告诉她我待会儿回电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes? I'm aware of that. No. Tell her I'll call her right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.77,0:29:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给你两分钟  刚刚是杜兰特国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two minutes. Secretary Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:29:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在外面等你给她回电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can wait outside for you to call her back --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.74,0:30:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我们说完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, let's finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.73,0:30:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你打算发表这些内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you decide to print any of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.24,0:30:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真能找到愿意发表的出版机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}assuming you find an outlet that's willing to,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  确实会让我头疼一阵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then, yes, it might cause me a headache for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.95,0:30:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会做出回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I will not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.59,0:30:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来  只会更加突出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think it will only prove to highlight
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,古德温先生的论断多么可笑  我同情他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how ridiculous Mr. Goodwin's claims are. I pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真心的  我觉得他需要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I truly do. I think he needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.71,0:30:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我采访过很多精神异常的人  他没疯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've interviewed many mentally ill people. He's not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.01,0:30:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你把自己的文章再好好读读\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I would suggest that you read your own article again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.54,0:30:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是非常痛苦  这两者是有区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's distressed. There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.87,0:30:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解  看到他入狱对你打击一定很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I understand. It must be a terrible blow to see him in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.26,0:30:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.88,0:30:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋·波斯纳确有其人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel Posner exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.31,0:30:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到她  但我已经证实她不是捏造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't been able to find her, but I've proven she's not a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.55,0:30:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊·科佩尼科也是  这些人确实存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same goes for Roy Kapeniak. These people were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.98,0:30:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有社保号码  既往住址...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have social security numbers, past addresses, past --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.40,0:30:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,全美各地的每个人都是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so does everyone from California to Maine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.37,0:30:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他们都有共谋吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I conspired with all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.11,0:30:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你得承认  酒驾问题确实有些解释不清的细节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to admit there are some troubling details regarding the DUI.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  人们也是这么说51区的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, people say the same thing about Area 51.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}有很多军事及外星人传闻的地区  美国政府对此既不肯定也不否认
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.77,0:30:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以尽情想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can conjure up little gray men if you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.12,0:30:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了彼得·罗素吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you kill Peter Russo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.68,0:31:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆  你这就是自找没趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, you're embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.54,0:31:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了佐伊·巴恩斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you kill Zoe Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.46,0:31:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些荒唐事根本不值得我浪费这么多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've given you more time than this nonsense deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.62,0:31:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to ask these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.75,0:31:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要我提问的话  我只问一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the only question I would ask is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.45,0:31:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的报道对古德温先生有利还是有害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}does this sort of article hurt or help Mr. Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.81,0:31:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你得做你认为对的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to do what you think is -- is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.35,0:31:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我希望你能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I hope you can understand
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.73,0:31:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法认真对待这些问题  有损我的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I don't demean myself by taking any of it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.41,0:31:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您抽出时间  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate your time, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.51,0:31:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务完成了  把这事了结了吧  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did my part. Now put it to bed, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.81,0:31:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会允许自己再面对这样的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't submit myself to this sort of exposure again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.51,0:31:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.09,0:31:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克和总统见面了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has Tusk met with the president yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.99,0:31:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,琳达说他们约了四点半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linda said they're meeting at 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.45,0:31:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,联系雷米  确保他上飞机前我能见他一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call Remy. Make sure he doesn't get on his plane before I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.72,0:31:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这就去办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.50,0:32:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沃克夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mrs. Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.13,0:32:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想说  我非常荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanted to say how rewarding it's been,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.03,0:32:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能在白宫西楼工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working here in the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.18,0:32:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为您丈夫工作  我很自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm so proud to be working for your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.70,0:32:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  我知道他赏识你的勤奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. I know he appreciates all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.21,0:32:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我现在在他身边工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, now that I'm working so closely with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.50,0:32:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么我能帮到您的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if there's anything I can do for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.43,0:32:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,任何能帮您或他减轻负担的事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything that would make yours or his life easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.40,0:32:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,继续做好你的工作就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keep doing what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.64,0:32:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真心的  您别客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Truly, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.45,0:32:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让您知道  你们可以依靠我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to know you can rely on me. Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.93,0:32:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  谢谢  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that. Thank you, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.25,0:32:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  沃克夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Mrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我来    -没事  我手不太听使唤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, here. Let me.   - Oh, it's just my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.01,0:32:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-很难受吗    -是啊  今晚估计要下雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are they bothering you?   - Yeah. Probably gonna get rain tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.50,0:32:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.16,0:33:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  继续搅拌肉汤就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, no. Just, uh, keep the broth moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.49,0:33:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是联调局的格林特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Green, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.14,0:33:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有空吗  斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a moment, Ms. Skorsky?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.98,0:33:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.09,0:33:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把炉子关了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need to turn the stove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-待在这儿  妈妈    -是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Stay in here, Mom.   - Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.92,0:33:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,待在这儿就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.50,0:33:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那一次吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only that once?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.76,0:33:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我就没见过他了  也没回他电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I haven't seen him since, or returned his calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.82,0:33:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他几次试图联系你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many times has he tried to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.14,0:33:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  大概八九次吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Eight or nine times, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,之后他消停了一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then he stopped after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.75,0:33:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他提到过机器人希洛尼摩斯或嘉文·奥尔西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he mention anything about Hieronymus Bot or Gavin Orsay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.67,0:33:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我该找个律师来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I think I should talk to a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.84,0:33:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们并不怀疑你是同谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now you're not suspected of being an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.47,0:33:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你找律师  那我们就要考虑一下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you call a lawyer, we might have to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.54,0:33:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-他提到了个黑客    -希洛尼摩斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He mentioned some hacker.   - Hieronymus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.05,0:33:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他  联系那个人不是什么好主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told him I thought it was a bad idea to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.92,0:34:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他所持的论调吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you aware of what he's claiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.44,0:34:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.21,0:34:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来在跟他合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you and he were working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.61,0:34:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他那套阴谋论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you believe in this conspiracy theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你收到了巴恩斯女士的私密照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That it was you who received explicit photos of Ms. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是真的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is any of that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.21,0:34:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你得跟我们回华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need you to come back to D.C. with us
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.99,0:34:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在联邦检察官的见证下签署这份声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sign this statement in the presence of the U.S. attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你们想让我指证他说谎吗    -他没有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want me to call him a liar.   - Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.83,0:34:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这样对他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't do that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.26,0:34:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你还得和汤姆·汉默施密特谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We also need you to speak with Tom Hammerschmidt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.98,0:34:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你们  能别把我扯进来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? Please, can you just keep me out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.49,0:34:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那个黑客毫无瓜葛...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with the hacker or the...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.51,0:34:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,斯克斯基女士  我们愿意相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ms. Skorsky, we want to believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你写下来我们就相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we will if you put all of it in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.93,0:34:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他没犯罪  你们查错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not a criminal. You're going after the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.55,0:34:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们认为你们能吓唬我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you think that you can intimidate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.71,0:34:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在我自己家这样骚扰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}harass me like this in my own home,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我会提出正式投诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will file a formal complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.78,0:34:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你语气越来越像他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're starting to sound an awful lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.11,0:35:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不能逮捕我  我什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't arrest me. I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.81,0:35:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.41,0:35:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权请律师  而且你们没有逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a right to legal counsel, and you haven't presented a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以逮捕你  斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can arrest you, Ms. Skorsky,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,以教唆网络恐怖主义的名义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for abetting an act of cyber terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.37,0:35:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你接下来三年都耗在法庭里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's going to take care of your mother while you're
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.30,0:35:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来照顾你母亲呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spending the next three years in courtrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.09,0:35:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦您抬手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you please raise your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.25,0:35:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-密查姆就不用了    -先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, Meechum.   - Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.98,0:35:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,密查姆  我知道你不想跟我握手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meechum. I know you don't want to shake my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.51,0:35:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就直接略过吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we'll just skip that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.32,0:35:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总统完全没有提\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president didn't mention anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.77,0:35:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么要提  抓你个冷不丁更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would he? The better to catch you off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.31,0:35:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要提\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.10,0:35:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好避免不必要的冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we can avoid unnecessary conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.63,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特可不会撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett's not a good liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真正会说谎的人总是让人觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The gift of a good liar is making people think
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.72,0:35:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他天生不会说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you lack a talent for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.01,0:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我远比你了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know him far better than you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.91,0:35:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他天生会什么  不会什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so I know what talents he has and lacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.92,0:35:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但假设他确实说谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But let's assume he did lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.47,0:35:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不担心联邦能源监管委员会的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not intimidated by a FERC investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.53,0:36:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,听证会还没开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd have grid overload and brown-outs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.23,0:36:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就会出现电网过载  灯火管制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before you could even get a hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.75,0:36:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在蓄意抬高电价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are deliberately keeping electric prices at inflated rates,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.38,0:36:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.62,0:36:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这是对自由市场的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I'm responding to free market.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是受监管的自由市场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A regulated free market.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.69,0:36:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么做  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you doing this, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.51,0:36:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米也这样问过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy asked me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是故意找我茬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're making this about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.59,0:36:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是针对你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't personal, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.05,0:36:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能源市场的健全是我唯一在乎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The integrity of our energy markets is my only concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.68,0:36:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然是针对我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course it's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.47,0:36:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你说服加勒特不再与中国针锋相对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked you personally to convince Garrett to pull back from China.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而你偏偏跟我对着干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You personally chose not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.81,0:36:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你还故意破坏峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You personally sabotaged the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.25,0:36:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我政治生涯中从未\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have never once in my political career
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.25,0:36:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你还让内阁把我逼上绝路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you personally advised the cabinet to push me up against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.27,0:36:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}因私人感情而耽误正事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}allow personal feelings to get in the way of pragmatic --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.55,0:36:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我耍花招  弗兰克  我耍不动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not try and spin me, Frank. I am too old to tango.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.76,0:36:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就直说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I'll be blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.97,0:36:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,接受核能补助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accept the subsidies
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.35,0:36:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就面对能源委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or deal with FERC.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.15,0:36:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有第三条路可选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no third way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是故意想毁掉总统吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you intentionally trying to destroy the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:37:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想保护总统  免受你的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to protect the president. From you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.65,0:37:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在为国务卿提名的事报复我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about the secretary of state nomination, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.14,0:37:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在是副总统了  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the vice president now, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.50,0:37:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会为陈年往事掉泪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't cry over what happened in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.57,0:37:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我力保你  你才当上副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're vice president because I vouched for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.89,0:37:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you had no other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.58,0:37:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是政治需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Political necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给你24小时做决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have 24 hours to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.62,0:37:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用送了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll show myself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.67,0:37:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.43,0:37:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  这是克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, this is Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.68,0:37:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人  见到你很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood, it is an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.46,0:37:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子珍  很欣赏你最近做出的种种努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jean-- my wife-- has been very taken with your recent efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.91,0:37:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,改天我一定要见见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd like to meet her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.41,0:37:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信她肯定非常愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She would very much like that, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.73,0:37:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么看呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.06,0:37:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.33,0:37:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最近在做的事  你怎么看呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are your thoughts about our recent efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.23,0:37:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,防止不必要的暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. I am in favor of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.17,0:37:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that prevents unnecessary violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.07,0:37:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nice to meet you, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.25,0:38:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你今晚开球好运  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, good luck with that first pitch tonight, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.48,0:38:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这次要投进本垒板  夫人再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make it to the plate this time. Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.40,0:38:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这防弹背心真不舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This Kevlar is cooking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.37,0:38:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得穿  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to use it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我练习时没穿过  这下胳膊都转不动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I didn't practice with it, and now I can hardly rotate my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.00,0:38:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我该提醒您的  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have mentioned it. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.33,0:38:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这球要是过不了本垒板  我拿你是问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this ball doesn't make it over the plate, it's your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.99,0:38:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干什么  没事可做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what are you doing here? Don't you have things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.54,0:38:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没来过卡姆登球场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never been to Camden Yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.96,0:39:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  马上将投出今晚第一球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, here to throw out the first pitch tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.52,0:39:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有幸请上  美国副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are honored to introduce the vice president of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.63,0:39:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.73,0:39:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  密查姆的球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boss, boss. Meechum's ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  吉祥物呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much. Where's the mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.95,0:39:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唱得真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautifully done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.96,0:39:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚很热  大家都想赶快看比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I know it's a hot night and you all want to get to the baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.23,0:39:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我一投出这玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So as soon as I throw this sucker,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.97,0:39:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家就喝点东西  享受比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}grab a drink, enjoy the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.93,0:39:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,祝两队好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and best of luck to both teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.54,0:39:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我收回那句话  这是在卡姆登球场啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scratch that. We're at Camden Yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.71,0:39:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,金莺队加油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go Orioles!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.37,0:40:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快走  快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.63,0:40:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是控制节点的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm told the distribution line that controls
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.98,0:40:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,配电线路造成了供电中断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the pinch point caused the outages.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.62,0:40:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,贝科  你的一家公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}BAPCO. One of your companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  电量出问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. There was a capacity issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.53,0:40:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人在以最快速度抢修\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're working as quickly as we can to resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有三位州长给我打过电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I've got three governors calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.34,0:40:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,医院在用应急电源  你们最好尽快修理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hospitals on emergency power. So quickly better mean quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.28,0:40:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最快也要2到3个小时  也许能快些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The latest estimate I got was two to three hours, maybe sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.70,0:41:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  这是故意的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, was this intentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.51,0:41:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我知道你最近不怎待见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I know you don't hold me in the highest regard at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.97,0:41:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你居然会这么想  我很吃惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am alarmed that you could even entertain such a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.21,0:41:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但这时候出现这种事让人很难相信是巧合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, the timing makes coincidence hard to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.27,0:41:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是热浪的缘故  热浪会让电网达到使用极限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a heat wave. That always pushes the grid to its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.32,0:41:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  快让人们摆脱黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get the people out of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.51,0:41:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,每30分钟报告一次进展情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Updates every 30 minutes on your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.24,0:41:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我要通知你  我明天可能要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should inform you, sir, that I may need to take
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.59,0:41:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭两座电厂做不定期维修\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}two of my plants offline tomorrow for unscheduled maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.43,0:41:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  哪两座厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? Which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.66,0:41:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,佐治亚州和田纳西州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Georgia and Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.19,0:41:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这次停电使这两座厂的负荷很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This blackout has put a great deal of stress on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.94,0:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工程师们担心燃料棒密封条破损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My engineers are concerned about the seals on the fuel rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.96,0:41:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么东南部也要断电吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we're looking at outages on the southeast grid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.45,0:41:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能  几天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be. For a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.04,0:41:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝对不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.15,0:41:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,安全第一   我们不希望出事故\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Safety comes first. We don't want an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.14,0:41:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  详细情况报告给琳达  尽快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get a full report to Linda, ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.62,0:41:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.47,0:41:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他在耍花招\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's toying with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.56,0:41:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不  或许真有这样的安全问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, this could be a legitimate safety issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他想夺回权力  那几个电厂没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants a seat back at the table. Those plants are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.36,0:42:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么这么做  我们的确有分歧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is he doing this? We've had our differences,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.12,0:42:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但非要做出这么偏激的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but something drastic like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.12,0:42:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他说了能源委员会可能会展开听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I did tell him about the possible FERC action.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.43,0:42:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.20,0:42:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他打电话给我  我接了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he called me. I answered the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.42,0:42:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不立即通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you inform me immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.44,0:42:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你们的谈话很有成效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He told me you had a productive talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他同意核能补助的事  我以为你们谈妥了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That he was on board with the subsidy. I assumed everything was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.05,0:42:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他提议进行新一轮贸易谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was proposing renewed trade talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.39,0:42:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们根本没谈核能补助的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't talk about the subsidy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.23,0:42:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他把我们俩都给耍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's playing both of us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.24,0:42:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他说他同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he told you he was on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.70,0:42:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么还提能源委员会的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why'd you bring up FERC?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.00,0:42:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我说这下我放心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told him I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.91,0:42:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他不答应  我们可要采取行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That we could have taken action if he didn't comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.88,0:42:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他是在套你的话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think he's fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.23,0:42:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想套出我们下一步行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To see what our next move might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.27,0:42:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so, sir. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.60,0:42:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,南部两个发电厂的事他在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he is lying about those two plants in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.95,0:42:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能猜测  一定要确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we can't guess. We have to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.68,0:42:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让雷蒙德·塔斯克来做风险评估\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, do you want Raymond Tusk to assess that risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.55,0:42:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还是政府来做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the United States government?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.28,0:42:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我们接管他的电厂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting we take over his facilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有过这样的先例\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is precedent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.02,0:42:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,伍德罗·威尔逊接管铁路三年整\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woodrow Wilson did it with the railroads for three full years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.99,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是战争时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a time of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.76,0:42:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是在危急时期  就像现在这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a time of emergency, which is what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.18,0:43:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,人民需要一位领袖  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The country needs a leader, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.36,0:43:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,满足他们  别向雷蒙德·塔斯克屈服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give them one. Do not bend to Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.81,0:43:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.81,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过你可能不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said you might not like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我看起来像是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It makes me seem crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.75,0:43:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最收敛的版本了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the most toned-down version.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.75,0:43:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力用最和善的口吻  不掺入偏见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried to be as kind as I could without being biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.81,0:43:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不希望这报道公诸于众吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think you want this going out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.61,0:43:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我能和简宁谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I talk to Janine?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,让他走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.51,0:43:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.95,0:44:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说了谎    -卢卡斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You lied.   - Lucas...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.60,0:44:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗了汤姆  也骗了联邦检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lied to Tom. You lied to the U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.14,0:44:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不知道还能怎么办    -说真话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't know what else to do.   - Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.64,0:44:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会逮捕我  他们会让我失去信誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll arrest me. They'll discredit everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.71,0:44:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,到时  人们会像不相信你那样不相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nobody is going to believe me more than they believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.95,0:44:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们能让公众知道  让人们产生疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we can get the story out there. Get people asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.54,0:44:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他们只会觉得我们俩都疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It'll just look like two crazy instead of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.48,0:44:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你打算自保\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're saving yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.21,0:44:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想保护我们两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to save the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.35,0:44:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.42,0:44:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,认罪吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.10,0:44:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是无罪的    -你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not guilty.   - You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.87,0:44:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你犯了罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.60,0:44:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-罪名还不只一项    -但不包括谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Multiple crimes.   - Not murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.88,0:44:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,承认罪行  好好表现  早点出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the plea. Be good. Get out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.10,0:45:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都坑我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody -- everybody's fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.11,0:45:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是想害你  就不会来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I was trying to fuck you I wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.98,0:45:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他要逃脱罪责了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna get away with it, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.03,0:45:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.53,0:45:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-有加冰的茶吗  给我一杯    -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take an iced tea if you have any.   - We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.35,0:45:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不想总这样偷偷摸摸的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I didn't have to keep coming through back doors like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.77,0:45:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是不想让新闻界的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we wouldn't want our friends in the fourth estate
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.62,0:45:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你来这里嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to know you were here, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.14,0:45:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是你费了好大的功夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Especially since you've gone to such lengths
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.17,0:45:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一直置身政治斗争之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to remain above the fray of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.95,0:45:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能夺走发电厂  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't seize the plants, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.11,0:45:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还没得手呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We haven't seized anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.64,0:45:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有这准备  但只要你合作就不会那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're ready to, but we won't if you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.99,0:45:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.98,0:45:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,并不违法  你心里清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.09,0:46:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急情况下  总统可以下达行政命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president can issue an executive order in times of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.21,0:46:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在法庭上据理力争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll fight it in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.38,0:46:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那比能源委员会的调查更费时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which will take even longer than a FERC investigation would.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.74,0:46:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而在此期间  你的发电厂无法盈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the meantime, you make nothing from those plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.41,0:46:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.74,0:46:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里  我们达成了协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right here in this room, we agreed to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.38,0:46:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,做出了合作的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We agreed as men of our word.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.20,0:46:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直信守承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I held up my end of that bargain
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.83,0:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可你在法案的事上背信弃义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you abandoned me on the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.97,0:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我让雷米去协助你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sent Remy to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.75,0:46:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是法案通过参议院之后  你之前可没帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After I got it passed through the Senate with no help from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.09,0:46:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能和总统闹僵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to protect my relationship with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.50,0:46:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,斯波特瑟尔韦尼亚峰会期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you tried to use me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.48,0:46:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你还企图利用我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}during the summit in Spotsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.09,0:46:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着不是为了做你最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was not put on this earth to be your best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.42,0:46:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是为了和你分享我的所有情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or to share every piece of information I have with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.57,0:46:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是达成了互利共赢的合作关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We agreed to a mutually beneficial partnership. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.36,0:46:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  而我现在发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. And what's become very clear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.49,0:46:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你合作对我没有任何好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that I benefit in no way from this partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.14,0:46:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就不装傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not pretend to be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.48,0:46:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最看重的都是个人利益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both respect self-interest above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.78,0:47:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  双方利益不再一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our versions of that no longer align.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.17,0:47:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要犯下无法挽回的错误了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are on the verge of making an irreversible mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.08,0:47:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.66,0:47:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确可能是在犯错  谁知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may well be making a mistake. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.08,0:47:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道你会联系琳达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I do know is that you'll be calling Linda
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.78,0:47:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她你接受核能补助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and telling her that you'll accept the subsidies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.43,0:47:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你有钱  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may have all the money, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.41,0:47:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have all the men with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.05,0:47:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是设好号码的一次性电话  她在等你答复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a burner, pre-dialed. She's expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.65,0:47:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  这是昨晚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, and, uh, yes. From last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.44,0:47:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,按行话说  现在轮到你发球了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ball's in your court, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.13,0:47:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝  你吓死我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jesus Christ. You scared the shit outta me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.10,0:48:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么随随便便地喊上帝吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you supposed to take the lord's name in vain like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.97,0:48:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,继续开着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.10,0:48:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,电费太贵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It costs too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.49,0:48:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我会付的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.98,0:48:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,古德温认罪了  他要进监狱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodwin took the plea. He's going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.77,0:48:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一切都结束了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So does that mean this is all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.78,0:48:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我们还是要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. We still have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.33,0:48:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  没有他  就不会有人找我了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But why? If he's gone, then nobody's looking for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.83,0:48:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,据我们所知没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.80,0:48:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在确保万无一失之前  一切照常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until we know, nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.20,0:48:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那你来就是为了让我空欢喜一场吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what, you just came over here to get my hopes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.21,0:48:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是为了确保你今晚不去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came here to make sure that you don't go to church tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.79,0:48:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to fuck me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.27,0:48:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-这才是你的本意吧    -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that what this is all about?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.96,0:48:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前干过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.46,0:48:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.80,0:49:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.84,0:49:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向能察觉男人对我的欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's one thing I know, it's when a man wants me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.09,0:49:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在教会得知了拉结的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I learned who Rachel was in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.09,0:49:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}拉结是《圣经》中和瑞秋同名的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.44,0:49:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她年轻漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was young and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.48,0:49:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,雅各在她照看羊喝水时爱上了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jacob fell in love with her while she was watering a lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.24,0:49:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他做了七年的工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she became his wife after he worked seven years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.73,0:49:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,才终于娶到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to earn her hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.82,0:49:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拉结有个叫约瑟的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel had one son. Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.94,0:49:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,后来他成了国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He became a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.99,0:50:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿不饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you hungry?
